Rosegarden sound module v0.1

18.6.2001

At a reasonable stage to check in the initial code for the
sound subsystem for Rosegarden.  At the moment this code is
not integrated with the main rosegarden code - examples of
how it is used can be found in the sound.c example file.

functionality:

 - read and parse MIDI file to internal representation
 - connect recording client with aRts and read incoming events
